You can run it FINE on a 1.5GHz w Gefore3/64MB. That's with all the crazy eye candy turned on. Averages 24FPS (just like any movie you ever see, good enough to be playable). Any reviewer telling you to buy new hardware is probably getting kickbacks for selling high-end hardware to folks who don't know better.
